Module it.polimi.ingsw
Package it.polimi.ingsw.view

Class GameView

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.view.GameView
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class GameView
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
Represents a view of the Game class to the client. It implements serializable so that it can be serialized in the messages that client and server exchange: this way, the client won't have access to the Model objects.
